metadata.name: Woodblock #10/30
metadata.description:
'Woodblocks' is a limited collection of 30 generative artworks inspired by traditional woodblock printing using noise, recursion, and flow fields.

Each piece is randomly generated within a custom 16 grid system via javascript. Traits include colour, texture, focus, joinery, frequency, and placement.

...

Dimensions - 3600x3600px
Format - JPEG
DPI - 300
Tool - p5.js
